      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial Motion-Law</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial Cam-Law, Motion-Law</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">When </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">all</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the segments are </text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, you can design complex </text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">and</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> simple motions.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion Description </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> motion-law is a powerful motion-law that can be used for most motion-designs.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You can edit the motion-values of all motion-derivatives at its start and its end.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You can also choose to &apos;not edit&apos; a motion-derivative at its start and end.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">It is used in the most complex motion-design problems when there are many motion-design constraints.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Values</text><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">CAN</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> edit the:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> at the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">END</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> at the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">End</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Acceleration</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> at the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">End</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Jerk</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> at the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Segment</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
